.turbo/

# Untracked local workspace notes and private docs.
# Exception: docs/adr/ holds the public Architecture Decision Records — the
# canonical decisions consumers see — so it IS tracked. `docs/*` (not `docs/`)
# keeps the directory itself unexcluded so the negation below can re-include it.
.claude/
.agents/
AGENTS.md
CLAUDE.md
docs/*
!docs/adr/
